AmeriTrust Corp said its boarddeclared a two-for-one stock split, and management intends torecommend to directors an increase in the quarterly dividend toat least 50 cts per share presplit from the current 44 cts.    The company said shareholders at the May 14 annual meetingwill be asked to approve an increase in authorized commonshares to 100 mln from 25 mln, as well as a limitation ofdirectors' liability and the establishment of a classifiedboard.    The split is subject to approval of the increase inauthorized common shares, it said. Reuter&#3;